{"tid":2506132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夏博義向英國推銷香港法治99%良好 反對英國法官辭任","createTime":"2021-04-27T06:18:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T07:28:41.000Z","uid":125168,"like":11,"dislike":77,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"46ea6dcdb6522a0db5ac447fd1ad78e2295cdb19","tid":2506132,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:18:02.000Z","msg":"夏博義向英推銷香港法制99%良好 翌日被中聯辦批鬥違法治<br />\n撰文: 記者林勵 | 發佈日期: 26.04.21<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/40686/夏博義-香港大律師公會-40686/夏博義\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F40686%2F%E5%A4%8F%E5%8D%9A%E7%BE%A9-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%83-40686%2F%E5%A4%8F%E5%8D%9A%E7%BE%A9&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=c87c05d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/40686/夏博義-香港大律師公會-40686/夏博義</a><br />\n<br />\n香港大律師公會主席夏博義上周六在英格蘭及威爾斯大律師公會網上會議上稱，「香港法律制度95-99%運作如常」，並重申反對海外法官辭任終審法院非常任法官，形容會是「最差」的情況。<br />\n<br />\n諷刺的是，夏博義向英國推銷香港法制一日後，就被中聯辦點名批評指他評論8.18及8.31兩案，指他「違背法治精神和法治原則」，質疑公會「縱容」夏博義繼續擔任主席，前特首梁振英及建制法律團體更點名要求夏博義辭去大律師公會主席一職。夏博義重申自己並非反華，但不願再進一步評論，只說香港仍然有亞洲最好的法律制度一日後，就被批評破壞法治是「有點諷刺」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合英格蘭及威爾斯大律師公會提供摘要，夏博義說，國安法令他不知道具體什麼可以說和不可以說，但強調「香港法律制度95至99%運作良好如昔」（95-99% of Hong Kong legal system operating as good as it has ever been），且仍然是亞洲中最有機會獲公平審訊的地方，不應將香港制度說成是腐爛。夏博義說，當中原因是因為香港終審法院由英國、澳洲及加拿大的傑出法官擔任，並提醒海外法官離任香港終審法院將是最差的情況，重申海外法官不應該辭任終院。<br />\n<br />\n他在回覆中強調： 「我也不是反中。自1986年首次到訪大陸後，我持續關注中國，全國只有兩個省份無踏足過，四度參與大律師公會訪京團，均是愉快及受啟發。我很抱歉中聯辦誤會，我歡迎有機會面對面澄清事件。」<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦質疑夏博義為暴力示威說項，諷刺的是，夏博義多次批評暴力行為。例如夏博義在2020年12月出版的《捍衛自由&mdash;&mdash;和平示威簡史》一書中，點名批評黃營「對參與者所犯的嚴重暴力行為也避而不談」，質疑2019年8月31日太子站有示威者被毀屍滅跡沒有可能。<br />\n<br />\n夏博義在書中表明：「假如，2019年夏秋兩季未曾發生持續暴力破壞，就絕不會有這部《國安法》。」"},{"pid":"4ba150ccba776336452e99385915ea2728160041","tid":2506132,"uid":125168,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:18:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1220cb45464e16e66dc64fc110277fceb43bd258","tid":2506132,"uid":363990,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:19:07.000Z","msg":"咁無咗果1-5%係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d215f6dc290a3bb1ad79e289d346149d2231f513","tid":2506132,"uid":18477,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:19:56.000Z","msg":"碌回力鏢返嚟嘅timing好到吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hair.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hair.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b376934594f7d049e8223abac5e310ad352a75d9","tid":2506132,"uid":126283,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:20:53.000Z","msg":"話人知99%良好同啲野99%新有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24dcc853eced2430a78f8d57348438e7417a36c7","tid":2506132,"uid":125168,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"d215f6dc290a3bb1ad79e289d346149d2231f513","tid":2506132,"uid":18477,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:19:56.000Z","msg":"碌回力鏢返嚟嘅timing好到吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hair.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hair.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c40eb5a31f54f14ccfc3e33c39d01322561b6703","tid":2506132,"uid":125168,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1220cb45464e16e66dc64fc110277fceb43bd258","tid":2506132,"uid":363990,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:19:07.000Z","msg":"咁無咗果1-5%係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb825d70fba85adebb24d3e41b6e04f193e1c3d","tid":2506132,"uid":189430,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:24:13.000Z","msg":"佢冇英國法官就俾唔到外國人睇香港有法治(做樣既法治)<br />\n人地自然就走,你見佢日日都話冇走資日日都話冇人移民<br />\n其實就係因為好撚多人走好撚多錢走佢咪日日講"},{"pid":"af580749dd4b6a2df43a863519b1bcc41d5adf6b","tid":2506132,"uid":59037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:26:04.000Z","msg":"竟然走黎怪抗爭者？班狗做得咁撚過份又唔講？"},{"pid":"269deab8c5f04c560e95dbc02dac3761797ea849","tid":2506132,"uid":340189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1220cb45464e16e66dc64fc110277fceb43bd258","tid":2506132,"uid":363990,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:19:07.000Z","msg":"咁無咗果1-5%係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:29:22.000Z","msg":"岩呀<br />\n香港法治99%良好冇錯呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過而家香港行中國人治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad33649959e2662476082961c53280ca3039f9ae","tid":2506132,"uid":316927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:29:58.000Z","msg":"689屌得佢啱<br />\n快撚啲辭職"},{"pid":"6c387cfc