官離任香港終審法院將是最差的情況，重申海外法官不應該辭任終院。<br />\n<br />\n他在回覆中強調： 「我也不是反中。自1986年首次到訪大陸後，我持續關注中國，全國只有兩個省份無踏足過，四度參與大律師公會訪京團，均是愉快及受啟發。我很抱歉中聯辦誤會，我歡迎有機會面對面澄清事件。」<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦質疑夏博義為暴力示威說項，諷刺的是，夏博義多次批評暴力行為。例如夏博義在2020年12月出版的《捍衛自由&mdash;&mdash;和平示威簡史》一書中，點名批評黃營「對參與者所犯的嚴重暴力行為也避而不談」，質疑2019年8月31日太子站有示威者被毀屍滅跡沒有可能。<br />\n<br />\n夏博義在書中表明：「假如，2019年夏秋兩季未曾發生持續暴力破壞，就絕不會有這部《國安法》。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:45:23.000Z","msg":"eg: 當有個國家有999條法律係正常冇問題，但有一條法律規定全國人民每日三餐都要食屎，唔食屎就要坐監。<br />\n咁呢個國家法制都係99%良好喎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76ddf76c7ea07e3d44f2d7d0d2a5b9d69078177","tid":2506132,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:45:30.000Z","msg":"狀棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n報應啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed9630244f1202d6ab4be8f1102bd48b884057d","tid":2506132,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e96c99b659a4832618ebfab3c8937a5e2cd56ba","tid":2506132,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986f7510287b5708615d7083557fca08503a9ace","tid":2506132,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:48:09.000Z","msg":"大陸佬終於識睇英國佬講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aea00bec0df43db5458de3829159ab5e055170f","tid":2506132,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df8c8b062b5868969769e849e4943a5ca03b558","tid":2506132,"uid":306914,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:49:14.000Z","msg":"夏博義說，國安法令他不知道具體什麼可以說和不可以說，但強調「香港法律制度95至99%運作良好如昔」<br />\n<br />\non9定弱智先講得出呢個邏輯"},{"pid":"e510d8b3ee7b30451f2bc891f819fb83022d8a61","tid":2506132,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7de27e050c7a80abc8080eb481088f293fe8d9c","tid":2506132,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"902e745fc23f0ede1c9cf81a284a18ddbc68c8b6","tid":2506132,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc79b913032480c953b778eada01560b7f68fc16","tid":2506132,"uid":47384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ba150ccba776336452e99385915ea2728160041","tid":2506132,"uid":125168,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:18:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T06:57:29.000Z","msg":"唔容許有人反駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63067f034cd4b739ed691273a3356f5b3dd07b99","tid":2506132,"uid":236171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b376934594f7d049e8223abac5e310ad352a75d9","tid":2506132,"uid":126283,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy